{"tid":1471502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支為被爆偽裝它牌手機 試圖在美銷售","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:01:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb692fe2087737c4f16e50ec027fbde09f0f0f6","tid":1471502,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"全球第2大智慧手機大廠中國華為（Huawei）被爆出，該公司為規避美國政府的禁令，正暗中將旗下手機偽裝成他牌手機，試圖在美國銷售。 《華盛頓自由燈塔》報導，美國情報機構示警，指出發現華為將旗下大量手機運往墨西哥，重新貼上標籤，試圖將華為手機偽裝成他牌手機，在美國銷售的計畫。 報導指出，這些換了標籤、偽裝成他牌的華為手機，仍然可以被識破。像是美國能透過檢查手機上的電子元件，追溯到這些偽裝手機是華為製的。 對此華為美國子公司，並未發表任何評論。"},{"pid":"d7834283bae11c7bee81dcb3570c62b0100c082f","tid":1471502,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"一批偽裝成手機嘅計時炸彈"},{"pid":"c96364864edecec97b34911bfcdfc8316001be13","tid":1471502,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"日本Ask<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4a0ed7207eb2ff3338f095e29c112252b07d1e","tid":1471502,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"66de6f045c44f3942d115bf33c2fae1184e877b7","tid":1471502,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本Ask<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d4ea05ea979c6afa895f27e40550586ff39171","tid":1471502,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bb692fe2087737c4f16e50ec027fbde09f0f0f6","tid":1471502,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"全球第2大智慧手機大廠中國華為（Huawei）被爆出，該公司為規避美國政府的禁令，正暗中將旗下手機偽裝成他牌手機，試圖在美國銷售。 《華盛